{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-js","path":"/creative/invitation/","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"id":"2303c599-1e51-569c-9e0b-cf63365d32a1","excerpt":"…","html":"<p>有一个朋友要结婚了，想找我做一个婚礼邀请函。他是一个程序员，想要自己的婚礼邀请函既能体现自己的职业特点，也要与众不同。</p>\n<p>我想了一下，说到程序员一般人会想到什么呢？那一定是一个人在屏幕前敲代码，所以我可以从敲代码入手。不如让这个邀请函一进来就是一个代码编辑器，而代码编辑器中有一段代码正在编辑，就好像打开邀请函的人看见了我的朋友在写代码。</p>\n<p><img src=\"/6be2b96544679d828850413dc1746280/start.gif\"></p>\n<p>当代码写完之后，就弹出一个正式的邀请函吧。</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 640px;\"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/b380b1e40cd98573507e0ceb814996fd/8ec0a/invite.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 80.625%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"invite\"\n        title=\"invite\"\n        src=\"/static/b380b1e40cd98573507e0ceb814996fd/c08c5/invite.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/b380b1e40cd98573507e0ceb814996fd/0913d/invite.jpg 160w,\n/static/b380b1e40cd98573507e0ceb814996fd/cb69c/invite.jpg 320w,\n/static/b380b1e40cd98573507e0ceb814996fd/c08c5/invite.jpg 640w,\n/static/b380b1e40cd98573507e0ceb814996fd/6a068/invite.jpg 960w,\n/static/b380b1e40cd98573507e0ceb814996fd/eea4a/invite.jpg 1280w,\n/static/b380b1e40cd98573507e0ceb814996fd/8ec0a/invite.jpg 2560w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 640px) 100vw, 640px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>点击邀请函，它就会自动展开，展示出里面的内页。这里，会有我朋友的结婚照，以及相关的婚礼信息。你可能会注意到，在内页中还有一个输入框可以写下祝福语。</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 640px;\"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/5d63d18010c08a5be19b6fa66439c4cd/8ec0a/wish.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 80.625%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"wish\"\n        title=\"wish\"\n        src=\"/static/5d63d18010c08a5be19b6fa66439c4cd/c08c5/wish.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/5d63d18010c08a5be19b6fa66439c4cd/0913d/wish.jpg 160w,\n/static/5d63d18010c08a5be19b6fa66439c4cd/cb69c/wish.jpg 320w,\n/static/5d63d18010c08a5be19b6fa66439c4cd/c08c5/wish.jpg 640w,\n/static/5d63d18010c08a5be19b6fa66439c4cd/6a068/wish.jpg 960w,\n/static/5d63d18010c08a5be19b6fa66439c4cd/eea4a/wish.jpg 1280w,\n/static/5d63d18010c08a5be19b6fa66439c4cd/8ec0a/wish.jpg 2560w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 640px) 100vw, 640px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>写下祝福语，按回车就可以发送出去啦。</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 640px;\"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/5d33565925314fdb529ca349a540bdfc/8ec0a/barrage.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 80.625%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"barrage\"\n        title=\"barrage\"\n        src=\"/static/5d33565925314fdb529ca349a540bdfc/c08c5/barrage.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/5d33565925314fdb529ca349a540bdfc/0913d/barrage.jpg 160w,\n/static/5d33565925314fdb529ca349a540bdfc/cb69c/barrage.jpg 320w,\n/static/5d33565925314fdb529ca349a540bdfc/c08c5/barrage.jpg 640w,\n/static/5d33565925314fdb529ca349a540bdfc/6a068/barrage.jpg 960w,\n/static/5d33565925314fdb529ca349a540bdfc/eea4a/barrage.jpg 1280w,\n/static/5d33565925314fdb529ca349a540bdfc/8ec0a/barrage.jpg 2560w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 640px) 100vw, 640px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>这就是我给朋友做的婚礼邀请函。</p>","frontmatter":{"title":"程序员结婚真可怕","date":"2019/02/23","description":"用代码定制一个邀请函。","color":"#151633","cover":"invitation.jpg","demo":"demos/invitation.png","demoText":null}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/creative/invitation/","previous":{"fields":{"slug":"/creative/find-two-elephants/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"不就是找对象嘛，我一分钟能找 100 个"}},"next":{"fields":{"slug":"/creative/brain-hole/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"脑洞没边儿"}}}}}